  <Docs>
    <summary>包含傳入至語音辨識引擎的音訊輸入的可能狀態的清單。</summary>
    <remarks>
      <format type="text/markdown"><![CDATA[  
  
## Remarks  
 您可以取得語音辨識引擎與音訊輸入的狀態<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognitionEngine.AudioState%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>和<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognizer.AudioState%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>屬性。 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognitionEngine.AudioStateChanged?displayProperty=nameWithType>和<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognizer.AudioStateChanged?displayProperty=nameWithType>音訊輸入語音辨識引擎變更狀態時，會引發事件。  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 下列範例會示範事件處理常式會處理變更音訊的語音辨識器狀態。  
  
```csharp  
  
private SpeechRecognitionEngine sre;  
  
// Initializes the speech recognition engine.  
private void Initialize()  
{  
  sre = new SpeechRecognitionEngine();  
  
  // Add a handler for the AudioStateChanged event.  
  sre.AudioStateChanged += new EventHandler<AudioStateChangedEventArgs>(sre_AudioStateChanged);  
  
  // Add other initialization code here.  
}  
  
  // Handle the AudioStateChanged event.  
  void sre_AudioStateChanged(object sender, AudioStateChangedEventArgs e)  
{  
  AudioState newState = e.AudioState;  
  
  // Handle event here.  
}  
  
```  
  
 ]]></format>
